data.description: This charming property, situated on a sprawling 16,265 sq ft lot, has been converted into four separate units, (original floor plan 3/3 ) making it a great investment opportunity or a multi-generational living solution. Each unit has its own private entrance and offers comfortable living spaces.  The expansive lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and future expansion. Create your dream backyard oasis, start a garden, or build additional structures ,build your dream pool, large lot big enough for RV, Boat , etc- the choice is yours!  Don't miss the opportunity to own this versatile property on a large lot in a desirable location. Whether you're looking for an investment has it all. Schedule a showing today and explore the potential of this unique property!
